These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea, cola, coffee
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, swimming, golf, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is golf##5
2. the person drinking iced-tea is not the person who's sport is climbing##6
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
6. the person who's sport is climbing is not the person drinking cola##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea   | coffee    | hot-chocolate    | cola |
| Sport      | snowboarding | climbing | golf | swimming |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, soy-milk, 7up, lemonade
There 4 different types of food: peach, nectarine, radish, strawberry
1. the person eating peach is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
3. the person eating strawberry is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5
4. the person drinking soy-milk is not the person eating nectarine##6
5. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
6. the person eating peach is on the right of the person eating radish##1
7. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
8. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk  | 7up    | almond-milk | lemonade    |
| Food       | strawberry | nectarine | radish  | peach |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk, lemonade, 7up
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, social-worker, pilot, photographer
1. the person drinking 7up is not the mechanic##6
2. the social-worker is not the person drinking lemonade##6
3. the pilot is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
4. the social-worker is the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the social-worker##1
6. the person drinking coffee is in an odd position##4
7. the mechanic is on the far left or far right##3
8. the pilot is somewhere to the left of the photographer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | 7up       | soy-milk  | coffee  | lemonade |
| Job        | pilot | photographer | social-worker | mechanic  |

