.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, pony, mouse, goat
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, ship, bus, snowmobile
1. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the person driving the car##5
3. the person driving the snowmobile is not the owner of the pony##6
4. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the right of the person driving the car##5
5. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
6. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | pony | mouse | goat     | cat |
| Transport   | ship     | bus    | car | snowmobile    |

