.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, hot-chocolate, juice, soy-milk
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, motorbike, train, airplane
1. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
3. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not the person driving the airplane##6
5. the person driving the van is not the person drinking tea##6
6. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
7. the person driving the train is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | tea        | soy-milk | juice | hot-chocolate |
| Transport   | airplane | van | motorbike     | train   |

