.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, animation, comedy, documentary
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, french, german, nigerian
1. the pakistani is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is not the french##6
3. the pakistani is on the far right##1
4. the french is somewhere to the right of the nigerian##5
5. the person watching comedy movies is the person watching comedy movies##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the pakistani##5
7. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching scientific movies##5
8. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5
9. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | comedy    | scientific  | documentary   |
| Nationality   | german  | nigerian | french | pakistani |

