.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, mystery, musical, drama
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, dubstep, folk, rock
1. the fan folk is on the left or right of the fan techno##3
2. the fan folk is not the person watching mystery movies##6
3. the person watching sports movies is the fan dubstep##1
4. the fan techno is on the left or right of the fan rock##3
5. the fan folk is on the far left##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is the fan techno##1
7. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the left of the fan techno##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | mystery     | musical | sports |
| Music-Genre   | folk | techno | rock      | dubstep         |

