3. the security-guard is on the right of the mechanic##1
4. the mechanic is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
5. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the mechanic##3
6. the electrician is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
7. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
8. the person drinking fanta is not the security-guard##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | fanta  | almond-milk        | sprite      | lemonade          |
| Job        | electrician | mechanic | security-guard | software-developer |

