.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, project-manager, doctor, writer
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, quad-bike, tram, snowmobile
1. the accountant is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the quad-bike is not the writer##6
3. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the doctor##5
4. the person driving the snowmobile is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
6. the person driving the snowmobile is the doctor##1
7. the accountant is not the person driving the snowmobile##6
8. the project-manager is somewhere to the right of the writer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | accountant  | doctor | writer    | project-manager |
| Transport   | quad-bike | snowmobile | tram | scooter  |

