.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, goat, lizard, turtle
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, biathlon, parkour, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is not the owner of the bird##6
2. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the owner of the lizard is not the person who's sport is ice-hockey##6
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is not the owner of the goat##6
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the lizard is the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | lizard | bird        | turtle  | goat     |
| Sport   | water-polo     | ice-hockey | biathlon | parkour |

