.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, video-games, sudoku, writing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, country, jazz, folk
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
2. the fan country is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
3. the fan jazz is not the person who's hobby is sudoku##6
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the fan folk and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
6. the fan country is between the fan r&b and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | sudoku | video-games    | skydiving | writing |
| Music-Genre   | r&b         | country | folk   | jazz     |

