.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-12::.
There 4 different types of food: pepper, peas, pineapple, carrot
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, scooter, train, helicopter
1. the person eating pineapple is somewhere to the right of the person driving the train##5
