3. the person driving the scooter is the person eating carrot##1
4. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person eating peas##1
5. the person driving the train is not the person eating carrot##6
6. the person eating peas is not the person driving the roller##6
7. the person eating pineapple is somewhere to the left of the person eating peas##5
8. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | pepper  | pineapple | peas | carrot |
| Transport   | train | roller     | helicopter     | scooter    |

