.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-13::.
There 4 different types of food: tomato, pepper, cucumber, lime
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, horror, animation, zombie
1. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the right of the person eating pepper##5
2. the person eating pepper is not the person watching horror movies##6
3. the person eating tomato is the person watching zombie movies##1
4. the person eating cucumber is somewhere to the right of the person watching horror movies##5
5. the person eating tomato is between the person eating pepper and the person watching family movies##2
6. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | lime | pepper      | tomato | cucumber   |
| Movie-Genre   | horror     | animation | zombie   | family |

