4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is between the firefighter and the person who's sport is soccer##2
6. the firefighter is not the person who's sport is ice-hockey##6
7. the nurse is on the right of the dressmaker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Job     | chef  | dressmaker | nurse | firefighter |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | soccer | golf   | snowboarding |

