4. the owner of the guinea-pig is not the person who's hobby is baking##6
5. the person who's hobby is camping is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
8. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the owner of the pony##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | dancing | camping | baking | puzzles |
| Pet     | cat  | pony      | goat  | guinea-pig       |

