4. the person driving the van is not the person drinking soy-milk##6
5. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person driving the jet-ski##5
6. the person driving the jet-ski is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | soy-milk | sprite | coffee      | lemonade   |
| Transport   | motorbike  | jet-ski   | car | van |

 